item.title: CVE-2019-0282|2024-08-04T17:44:16.560Z -- sap%20se -- sap%20netweaver%20process%20integration%20%28runtime%20workbench%29
item.description: Several web pages in SAP NetWeaver Process Integration (Runtime Workbench), fixed in versions 7.10 to 7.11, 7.30, 7.31, 7.40, 7.50; can be accessed without user authentication, which might expose internal data like release information, Java package and Java object names which can be misused by the attacker.
